  "remarks": "Jean Claude Habyarimana Mbitse holds a leading position as spokesperson of the “Collectif des mouvements pour le changement / Forces de défense du peuple” (CMC-FDP), a non-governmental armed group operating in Eastern DRC. In addition, Jean Claude Habyarimana Mbitse holds a leading position as spokesperson and liaison officer of the so-called “Wazalendo” or “Volontaires pour la Défense de la Patrie” (VDP), a coalition of non-governmental armed groups operating in Eastern DRC which fights against the coalition of M23/RDF/AFC.",
